headline: Uber, Consubanco, and Bkaya launch Uber Pro Card in Mexico: an innovative financial solution for drivers and couriers
summary: Uber, in partnership with Consubanco and Bkaya–a leading technology company in Mexico focused on embedded finance and financial inclusion– announces the launch of the Uber Pro Card program throughout Mexico. This innovative financial solution is designed to give drivers and couriers greater control over their earnings, more financial flexibility, and access to exclusive benefits.
